title._content: Hurricane and Flood of 1938, Keene NH - The First Congregational Church lost its steeple!

description._content: TITLE Hurricane and Flood of 1938, Keene NH - The First Congregational Church lost its steeple! CREATOR Parker, R.G., Keene NH SUBJECT Churches - NH - Keene Hurricanes - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION Photograph of the First Congregational Church, Central Square, Keene New Hampshire, which lost its spire during the height of the Hurricane of 1938. It crashed through the roof, narrowly missing the pipe organ.
